Global Liquid Eye Shadow Market Insights
Liquid Eye Shadow Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Liquid Eye Shadow Market Overview
The global liquid eye shadow market was valued at USD 3.22 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 5.21 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.2% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by increasing consumer demand for high-quality, long-lasting cosmetics that offer ease of application. Liquid eye shadows are gaining popularity due to their convenience, innovative formulas, and vibrant color options. The rising trend of multitasking products and the growing awareness about personal grooming and beauty are key contributors to the expansion of the market.

